DESCRIPTION:<2026-04-29 Wed 13:00-14:30>\n• ☑ HB: contact Glenda about mixi
 ng gases and running tubing.\n• ☐ HB: measure distance to determine length
  of 1/4 in PFTE tubing.\n  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
 ━━━━━━━━━━━━\n   Distance\, ft  Description\n  ───────────────────────────
 ────────────────────────────────\n              2  Valve to counter edge\n
               6  From valve going up to ceiling support\n             18  
 Across ceiling support\n              6  From ceiling support down to coun
 ter height\n              8  From support across to UV/vis spec\n  ───────
 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n             40  Tot
 al\n  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
